description: FIGURES 285–288. Interspecific variation in proportions (285–286) and absolute sizes (287–288) of selected characters in the Calapnita vermiformis group. These graphs are based on measurements of holotypes and ignore intraspecific variation. The graphs show the conspicuous but largely continuous interspecific variation in some male genital characters.
name: FIGURES 285–288 in Revision and cladistic analysis of the Southeast Asian leaf-dwelling spider genus Calapnita Simon (Araneae, Pholcidae)
